The following method is used to count shifts during insertion sort.

```java
public static int countShifts(int[] a)
{
    int count = 0;
    for (int j = 1; j < a.length; j++)
    {
        int temp = a[j];
        int possibleIndex = j;
        while (possibleIndex > 0 && temp < a[possibleIndex - 1])
        {
            a[possibleIndex] = a[possibleIndex - 1];
            possibleIndex--;
            count++;
        }
        a[possibleIndex] = temp;
    }
    return count;
}
```

